{"tid":1575171,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有朋友跳狗鐵比人督灰","createTime":"2019-09-16T17:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T18:05:49.000Z","uid":55818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6d07a3efc9508d9bc407320bf4ec24fa7ff65bda","tid":1575171,"uid":55818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:28:35.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味一跳完有個死廢老去同個黃衫廢老話我朋友跳閘<br />\n佢陰聲細氣叫我朋友去check飛<br />\n我朋友扮好合作跟佢去<br />\n朋友半路行到條樓梯到就跑走左 個廢老一路追 跌左一次銀包執返都走到<br />\n最後我朋友去左第二個出口再跳多次搭走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後跳嘅小心埋d死藍絲廢老<br />\n有咩唔對路跑走佢就淨係可以係出口望住你 話你跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以根本唔洗驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋今日見到 油麻地站碧街個出口就已經有6個職員企左係到 有紅衫有黃衫 唔知狗鐵要比多幾多錢捉人跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友決定繼續再跳 大家都一齊陪我朋友跳好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b654dafb3e3f68d0de6cd4c125dca018a2a539f4","tid":1575171,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">星期三有大綱睇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rR6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=fd7a3683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagr